I have to disagree with this. CC is much better if you are trying to time it such that you can kill your pet in one nuke for full exp and get another pet. That is something that I can see done literally as often as you cast CoD while charm soloing. All you have to do is run in and stun the target so it won't damage your pet once your pet hits Nuke range. More than likely you can even use this to get the target to nuke range as well. Then you can Mez, Invis, Root, Nuke, Nuke and move on. </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

